result.formatted_address: 24 Boundary St, Mong Kok, Hong Kong
result.name: Ki Lung Tea Restaurant

reviews.text: Highly recommend the space, was brought here by a friend of mine. The food here is very good, very Hong Kong style to but I’m mixture of western by the Hong Kong twist and pure Chinese food. They have a great menu here, and the staffs are very kind even though they’re very short staffed. Would recommend coming for the steam fish especially, but do you order earlier as it takes time to cook.
Reasonable price and tastes very nice. No english  menu. The chicken should be ordered after 11:00 AM. 7:00-11:00 is breakfasts time.

People compliment for his kind heart to do charity. 

But the cashier throw back the remaining cash to me, so rude! 😡
Very good indeed.
One of the best 茶餐廳 I've tried to far.

result.name: 基隆茶餐廳

reviews.text: 佢有冇味精嘅例湯👍
第一次去，食物都ok, 侍應好。
老闆娘和藹可親，服務態度良好。地方整潔， 可以一試在試！ 今次試埋炸鯪魚球，非常好一定要試。
小店但相當多不同種類美食，店主亦是關心社稷之人，紥根的意義
具香港茶記特色，支持小店。小店為良心企業，有作不少善事，會繼續支持。
